ActFinancial Administration Act
Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Finance of LINDA CATY of Carignan, Quebec, to be a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Deposit Insurance Corporation, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of Shelley M. Tratch, whose term has expired.
